A simple and modern Blackjack game built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The game is designed to be user-friendly, visually appealing, and responsive. Play against the dealer and try to reach 21 without going over!

Features
Modern UI: A clean and responsive design for an enjoyable experience.
Game Logic:
Player and dealer take turns.
Dealer stands on a score of 17 or higher.
Player can hit (draw a card) or stand (stop drawing).
Win, lose, or tie based on Blackjack rules.
Interactive Controls: Intuitive buttons for Hit, Stand, and Restart.
Real-Time Scoring: Scores update dynamically as cards are drawn.
Preview

How to Play
Objective: Reach a score as close to 21 as possible without going over.
Hit: Draw another card.
Stand: End your turn and let the dealer play.
Win Conditions:
You win if your score is closer to 21 than the dealer's without exceeding 21.
Dealer busts by exceeding 21.

